OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,FHe was planning a legal challenge to
OL,7,Fthe Government after he was told he
OL,8,Fwas 'not British' and would not be
OL,9,Fallowed indefinite leave to remain
OL,10,Fwhen he applied for a passport in 2019.
OL,12,FInstead officials told him he would
OL,13,Fhave to pay #7,000 to start the ten
OL,14,Fyear process of settlement.
OL,16,FHe came to the UK in 1977 from Ghana
OL,17,Fas a student, and went on to run a
OL,18,Fpopular newsagents in Wallasey as well
OL,19,Fas performing jury service and even
OL,20,Fgetting a police bravery award when he
OL,21,Fstepped in to stop a robbery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
