OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,FHis story was covered by ITV Granada
OL,7,FReports correspondent Tim Scott in May.
OL,9,FSpeaking after the decision to allow
OL,10,FNelson to remain he said: "All along I
OL,11,Fhad tried to bottle every feeling in
OL,12,Fme so that my children wouldn't be
OL,13,Fworrying about me.
OL,15,F"I was so relieved that in the end, we
OL,16,Fhave won the battle.
OL,18,F"Now we hope to win the war: for the
OL,19,Fauthorities to agree that the 10-year
OL,20,Froute is inhuman, and abolish it or
OL,21,Fshorten it".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
