OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,FHis sons Aaron and Jacob helped in the
OL,7,Fcampaign. Sitting with his Dad Jacob
OL,8,Fsaid they had been through tough times
OL,9,Fbut are now able to relax, taking
OL,10,FNelson to his favourite food place in
OL,11,Fcelebration.
OL,13,F"Dad's victory means the absolute
OL,14,Fworld to us. We are so grateful to our
OL,15,Flegal team at the Greater Manchester
OL,16,FImmigration Aid Unit and to everyone
OL,17,Fwho supported us throughout this
OL,18,Fprocess - from sharing our story to
OL,19,Fdonating, we cannot thank you enough".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
