OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,F"It wasn't an easy process to get
OL,7,Fhere: incorrect applications, a lack
OL,8,Fof legal advice, wrong information
OL,9,Ffrom the Home Office and 2 previous
OL,10,Frefusals to grant ILR.
OL,12,F"Despite this and despite the
OL,13,Fconsiderable financial risk to Nelson
OL,14,Fand his family he made the decision to
OL,15,Ffight on and speak out about the
OL,16,Finjustice he has experienced.
OL,18,F"Nelson's bravery in the face of a
OL,19,Fdysfunctional immigration system has
OL,20,Fbeen inspirational."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
